Features

Timezone detection and selection

Automatic detection of the user’s local time zone. Manual selection of additional zones from a list. Ability to add, edit, and remove global clocks from the display

Event management

Create, edit, and delete events. Assign events to specific time zones. Recurring events (daily, weekly, monthly, yearly). Event details (title, description, location, participants).

Timezone Converter

Convert specific dates and times between selected time zones. Simple and intuitive interface for quick conversions.
